name: ItemContainer
description: ItemContainer node, contains a list of items Examples of ItemContainers are Bank, Inventory, Equipment Known ID's can be found at ItemContainerId This will not set Item.getDestination() when building the items

methods.name: Item
methods.description: Gets the items in this item container Does not add empty slots to the list Does not set item destinations

methods.name: getItems
methods.description: Gets the items in this item container Does not add empty slots to the list Does not set item destinations
